%F A027961 a(n) = F(n) + F(n+2) - 3, n >= 2, where F(n) is the n-th Fibonacci number. - _Zerinvary Lajos_, Jan 31 2008
%F A027961 a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} ((-1/phi)^k + (phi)^k) where phi = 1/2+1/2*sqrt(5). - _Dimitri Papadopoulos_, Jan 07 2016
